U.S. General Accounting Office, FDA Drug approval--A Lengthy Process that Delays
the Availability of Important New Drugs, May 28, 1980.<p>

Viscusi, W. Kip, Reforming Products Liability, Harvard University Press, 1991.<p>

Viscusi, W. Kip, Michael J. Moore, and James Albright, "A Statistical Profile of
Pharmaceutical Industry Liability, 1976-1989," Seton Hall Law Review, 1994, pp.
1418-1436.<p>

Viscusi, W. Kip, Steven R. Rowland, Howard L. Dorman, and Charles J. Walsh,
"Deterring Inefficient Pharmaceutical Litigation:  An Economic Rationale for the
