<DOCOLDNO>IA034-000689-B008-89</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/pff/clean/end.html 204.71.237.88 19970209094915 text/html 35028
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 09:49:56 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:40 GMT
Content-length: 34842
